description: This table contains PDC quant data for Proteogenomics of Gastric Cancer - Proteome
friendlyName: PROTEOGENOMICS OF GASTRIC CANCER - PROTEOME QUANT DATA 2020_11

fields.name: aliquot_run_metadata_id
fields.description: Uniquely identifies the aliquot by how it was used in the experiment (based on the labelling reagent and/or biological replicate)

fields.name: aliquot_submitter_id
fields.description: Unique source id provided by the data submitter (e.g. looks like e5e1306b-719e-4c3e-b85b-fd1231_D2)

fields.name: study_name
fields.description: Name of the study (e.g. Pediatric Brain Cancer Pilot Study - Phosphoproteome)

fields.name: protein_abundance_log2ratio
fields.description: Average log-ratio of sample reporter-ion to common reference of peptide ions associated with the gene in acquisitions from a specific biological sample
